{"tid":1728823,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"ming仔又撚連登仔","createTime":"2019-11-17T04:37:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T06:44:19.000Z","uid":61348,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"92de09db17e63be580d500bf8cd685510e9df774","tid":1728823,"uid":61348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:37:19.000Z","msg":"回帶binc<br />\nming仔又撚連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/654961/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/654961/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"239d476ed67fb136dafddb8cc2857a697f24c99f","tid":1728823,"uid":297230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:43:23.000Z","msg":"他們在打的是「<strong>中共政權保衛戰</strong>」，而你們僅僅是在打「<strong>香港生活方式保衛戰</strong>」<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1728140/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1728140/page/1</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>（一） Be Water(水聚散) 不能變為Be Castle（碉堡戰、陣地戰）</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">對付Be Water，第一就是分化，把勇武派、和理非派拆分，第二步是下餌，引誘勇武派進入「必守的陣地」，刺激他們建立碉堡，最好所有的勇武派都集中進入少數陣地（例如四所大學），然後隔絕、撒網、一舉成擒。</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>（二） 從「誰才是暴徒」辯論陷阱脫身</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">港人對抗港府還算旗鼓相當，畢竟兩邊都是被法治洗禮過的香港人，但是港人對付中共的無底綫宣傳統戰技能，坦白說，還是太嫩。世人關心香港事態的焦點從「港人要自由、要自治」，變成「人民和政府誰才是暴力方」的辯論，這正是北京要製造的焦點轉移。</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">（三） 一切回歸三個字 &ndash; 真普選</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">核心訴求只有一個：真普選，一切口號、行動、宣傳，都環繞真普選這單一訴求展開，這樣，世界聽得懂，連中國內地人民都聽得懂。</span>"},{"pid":"64c03ca4e58fb6d2346753cfb3083399ce80a7b1","tid":1728823,"uid":14897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:48:39.000Z","msg":"其實佢係邊個 我真係唔識"},{"pid":"d9fbcdf0a03d7050a89dce958169eb369e72ae62","tid":1728823,"uid":17866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"64c03ca4e58fb6d2346753cfb3083399ce80a7b1","tid":1728823,"uid":14897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:48:39.000Z","msg":"其實佢係邊個 我真係唔識"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T05:07:06.000Z","msg":"成班小學雞以前最鐘意睇個班香港垃圾「YouTuber」之一嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：who ?"},{"pid":"42efc954e3df8fae8dd05a61e088fb0e0b442612","tid":1728823,"uid":189235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T06:44:19.000Z","msg":"個#3嗰陣仲要比人負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}